{"tid":2208200,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳芷尤塞愛犬入衫任踩胸　網民：想做你隻狗","createTime":"2020-09-18T16:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T18:10:03.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67410c79ca6d7a69a638ca2b25f7ae8a8afe48d4","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"陳芷尤離開無綫，返回家鄕新加坡發展演藝事業，拍電影又拍網劇，不過感情上唔似前度張振朗已有新戀情，閒時弄狗為樂，去邊都帶住愛犬Soju，在家更不時抱緊處理，相當肉緊，日前身穿t恤的陳芷尤將Soju塞入身上衫內，被焗住的Soju不停掙扎，狂踩陳芷尤34D心口，能夠同陳芷尤「人狗交融」，網民都紛紛留言：「想做你隻狗﹗」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/xoxoapo_116496449_624564778441891_1667519142422958669_n_16829799655f6460e7a1915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fxoxoapo_116496449_624564778441891_1667519142422958669_n_16829799655f6460e7a1915.jpg&h=bba6f6fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2e3c4c7b83fb4f341cb090cf3fe36ffd270923a","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/xoxoapo_118697545_305329177229855_762959207239633053_n_11035447395f6462854b90b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fxoxoapo_118697545_305329177229855_762959207239633053_n_11035447395f6462854b90b.jpg&h=28414bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出海一樣與狗同行。"},{"pid":"b4e4f9f88d405ea42da0248c1f4a82c9c95b9904","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"同張振朗拍拖五年突分手<br />\n<br />\n今年31歲，身形嬌小但上圍凸出有「小舒淇」之稱，11年參加港姐未能入圍，後加入藝訓班成為合約藝員，在無綫的工作大多要以身材做賣點，同張振朗拍拖五年一直唔認愛，18年突然在網上公告分手，翌年陳芷尤約滿無綫後便返回家鄉新加坡。"},{"pid":"6336acc297cd724d0108b8d2b663251e7b8afd7d","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_2672_2809612545f646130cdedc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fimg_2672_2809612545f646130cdedc.jpg&h=9a1c02b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日身穿粉紅上衣的陳芷尤，同愛犬Soju在家親子活動，把五個月大的松鼠塞入衫內，被困在內的狗狗不停對準主人心口狂踩。"},{"pid":"c300bdae8e02a3b630d113f69e942cba927e1716","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"任愛犬踩心口<br />\n<br />\n近月養了一頭松鼠狗Soju，依家5個月大，陳芷尤錫狗錫到燶，行街、歎Tea甚至滑水都帶埋愛犬，對住還是BB的Soju，陳芷尤相當肉緊，不時親嘴攬到實，日前著住粉紅色T恤的陳芷芷，將狗狗塞入衫內，被困住的Soju不停掙扎之餘，不停在陳芷尤身上狂踩，34D巨乳任由Soju狂踩，Soju幾經掙扎在衫領口捐個頭出來，陳芷尤立即錫錫獎勵，一眾網民留言「但願做隻狗」、「羡慕你的狗，不知你愿不愿意收留我這隻單身狗」、「狗狗可以吃奶奶」、「你的狗真幸福」。"},{"pid":"901af0002d6b9215cb83a922d26ab424dcbddc98","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_2674_10226423325f646167818ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fimg_2674_10226423325f646167818ea.jpg&h=a3721f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛犬不停在陳芷尤身上郁動，人狗相當親蜜。"},{"pid":"1e6c01a1e5e89deb0df52c5a976f41bae03824f8","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_2678_3853671915f64616ed1713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fimg_2678_3853671915f64616ed1713.jpg&h=4f29d04e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4fb58de52c187e7510e48c1d3bb674d032bf08d","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_2688_20656372515f64617543fd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fimg_2688_20656372515f64617543fd1.jpg&h=bc2d1174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3e6ecfa33d4bacebe3643ce47af1a772fb63354","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"新加坡當演員待遇比TVB好得多<br />\n<br />\n陳芷尤在新加坡發展演藝事業，發展順利，拍過電影又擔過女一，不用只以身材做賣點，發展明顯比在無綫時好，而且待遇大不同，陳芷尤曾在訪問中表示在新加坡，開工時間不會長於十二小時，每隔七天有一天休息，而且薪酬比在TVB多，佢話：「唔似喺TVB有開工冇收工﹗」所以未有回巢打算。"},{"pid":"39796e9f0d94a7081c4433d985d1406d210e8799","tid":2208200,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/img_2694_1402460245f6461a90e956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fimg_2694_1402460245f6461a90e956.jpg&h=267484bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一日，陳芷尤同愛犬Soju的親子活動，是人狗共舞，把Soju放上心口，34D巨乳成了Soju寬闊的平台，陳芷尤隨住立樂搖來搖去，Soju都唔會跌。"},{"pid":"fe75bd0cf9f251b9766e6d848851ef74d5409d5d","tid":2208200,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇失身俾朗朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6153d768f5e2f12d727d5cd8ed46bc3ec14f39","tid":2208200,"uid":240031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"一定有搵隻狗幫手奶西<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4588b22c03c0641aa484da911b0fe038303e0071","tid":2208200,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae6153d768f5e2f12d727d5cd8ed46bc3ec14f39","tid":2208200,"uid":240031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"一定有搵隻狗幫手奶西<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/fic3ENicVS1Hz4dEJWPGXibcySC7aSsrOw5ViaPK1DBLdAUUVdPAbeicOGsaAKjeS4EzRiaiansZWCNVnPpQtXoMBE5bg/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Ffic3ENicVS1Hz4dEJWPGXibcySC7aSsrOw5ViaPK1DBLdAUUVdPAbeicOGsaAKjeS4EzRiaiansZWCNVnPpQtXoMBE5bg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif&h=4a26fb9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b6ce1f036031870eeafdf95d1410e1b2fdea461","tid":2208200,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s9.rr.itc.cn/r/wapChange/20174_7_21/a6ddy32608971216619.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs9.rr.itc.cn%2Fr%2FwapChange%2F20174_7_21%2Fa6ddy32608971216619.gif&h=e2126ee4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a327f3a210be54efff83cbca2bc5271f15c15914","tid":2208200,"uid":194120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fe75bd0cf9f251b9766e6d848851ef74d5409d5d","tid":2208200,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇失身俾朗朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T17:30:51.000Z","msg":"有條咁嘅女點可能唔同佢做愛？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bs4f9rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBs4f9rw.jpg&h=b13f1ce6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab96ae740806a4eb94c0473e9acc01da82b0c8b3","tid":2208200,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"張振朗拍劇傷完條腰 就被陳芷尤飛咗 使唔使大食到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d98ffebafa510e700da86110a7f435cac26958","tid":2208200,"uid":96767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"條女好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}